The Story of Salvation
Want to understand God’s bigger plan in Scripture? Wondering how the stories in the Bible apply to your life? If so, this Bible study is for you and your group.  This Bible study has two main goals: that all participants know all 6 covenants, and that all participants know their place in God’s plan. This study has the added feature of video explanations to help the leader prepare quickly and effectively. Also, use the Lectio Divina Daily Reflections to help your group stay connected and pray throughout this study.
